www.benesse.co.jp/brand/category/art/20260424_1/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"sustaina_index_imgover\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sustaina_pic\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<source           srcset=\"/benesseinfo/sustainability/images/brand_20260424_1.webp\" type=\"image/webp\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"su-full\" src=\"/benesseinfo/sustainability/images/brand_20260424_1.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sustaina_txt su-fs\"><em>AI時代に必要な自分で考える力を磨く、新たな学び体験を。「問いの島」キャンプin 直島・豊島</em></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"sustaina_top_brand\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.benesse.co.jp/brand/category/contribution/20251107_1/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"sustaina_index_imgover\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sustaina_pic\"><img class=\"su-full\" src=\"https://www.benesse.co.jp/brand/assets/images/article/20251107_1/thumb.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sustaina_txt su-fs\"><em>体感したアートの力とは。企業価値向上とアートの関係を考えた「SETOUCHI企業フォーラム」</em></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"sustaina_top_brand\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.benesse.co.jp/brand/category/education/20250829_1/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"sustaina_index_imgover\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sustaina_pic\"><img class=\"su-full\" src=\"https://www.benesse.co.jp/brand/assets/images/article/20250829_1/thumb.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sustaina_txt su-fs\"><em>直島で、アートと対話し“自分を見つける”夏を。「14歳アートフェスin直島」</em></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"sustaina_top_brand\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.benesse.co.jp/brand/category/education/20250729_1/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"sustaina_index_imgover\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sustaina_pic\"><img class=\"su-full\" src=\"https://www.benesse.co.jp/brand/assets/images/article/20250729_1/thumb.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sustaina_txt su-fs\"><em>多様性や包括的性教育も。親子で楽しみながら世界を広げる『しまじろうのわお！』</em></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t<div><a href=\"https://www.benesse.co.jp/brand/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"view_more\">View More <img src=\"/assets_ren/images/icon-blank3.svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" alt=\"\"></a></div>\n\t\t</nav>\n\n\t\t<nav class=\"su-contents\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"sustaina_title\">直島での活動</h2>\n\t\t\t<p>｢Benesse（よく生きる）｣ 。この企業理念が誕生した原点でもある場所で、地域固有の自然や文化を大切にしながらアートや建築を融合。地域に暮らす人々と共に新しい価値を生み出し、この地に訪れる一人ひとりが「よく生きる」とは何かを考えるための活動を続けています。</p>\n\t\t\t<figure id=\"sustaina_top_naoshima\">\n\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/benesseinfo/sustainability/images/pic_200.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"c-button-type3 arw_ani\"><a href=\"/about/naoshima.html\">ベネッセアートサイト直島</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t</nav>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"su-contents_bg\">\n\t\t\t<nav class=\"su-contents\">\n\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"sustaina_title\"><span>ベネッセグループの</span><span>ESG活動</span></h2>\n\t\t\t\t<ul id=\"sustaina_top_nav\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"sustaina_top_nav-col\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"sustaina_top_nav-colpic\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/benesseinfo/sustainability/images/pic_egc_e.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"sustaina_top_nav-coltxt\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-textlink arw_ani\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/benesseinfo/sustainability/esg/environment/index.html\">環境</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"sustaina_top_nav-sub\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"su-link su-arr\"><a class=\"su-fs is-lineAni\" href=\"/benesseinfo/sustainability/esg/environment/management.html\">環境マネジメント</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"su-link su-arr\"><a class=\"su-fs is-lineAni\" href=\"/benesseinfo/sustainability/esg/environment/climate.html\">環境活動の推進</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"su-link su-arr\"><a class=\"su-fs is-lineAni\" href=\"/benesseinfo/sustainability/esg/environment/educat